{"tid":903655,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改革開放40週年展覽  習近平看板佔三分二 鄧江胡合計僅佔三分一","createTime":"2018-11-15T17:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T17:04:10.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"41ba1b0de9435e836f99a3d9506e4acb6289a76e","tid":903655,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"紀念改革開放40週年系列活動之一的「偉大的變革─慶祝改革開放40週年大型展覽」，近期在中國國家博物館舉行。11月14日展覽正式對公眾開放，據多維新聞報道，其中「關鍵抉擇」展區的看板中，鄧小平、江澤民、胡錦濤等中共前領導人的事蹟合計僅佔這一展區的1/3，其餘2/3都是習近平的事蹟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099271/org/4aaa628aeae3e6cc78b96adb713d5ba8.jpg/Bo7JDQZ8cCAUuCPMJ5rOEtR_3ZFgjyBJtflczrX5XM4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099271%2Forg%2F4aaa628aeae3e6cc78b96adb713d5ba8.jpg%2FBo7JDQZ8cCAUuCPMJ5rOEtR_3ZFgjyBJtflczrX5XM4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6cadb0ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有關習近平事蹟的介紹，集中在中共18大後至今的軍改授旗、從嚴治黨、依法治國等內容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099274/org/24f6b8be14df7ecfee3cf12c3917d521.jpg/X0kOcq22z5Dau_BFzyymSLcQtecqVsAXKwk98SsJPfE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099274%2Forg%2F24f6b8be14df7ecfee3cf12c3917d521.jpg%2FX0kOcq22z5Dau_BFzyymSLcQtecqVsAXKwk98SsJPfE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0d006961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於鄧小平的事蹟，有撥亂反正、改革開放、一國兩制、中英談判、南巡講話等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099275/org/ef569ea8d7de3115d349d94a3b2be5fe.jpg/R1pxeGckx8ZUBMQVUpWabZrAnUXqnHBucpRVVXKUVVU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099275%2Forg%2Fef569ea8d7de3115d349d94a3b2be5fe.jpg%2FR1pxeGckx8ZUBMQVUpWabZrAnUXqnHBucpRVVXKUVVU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f8ed2333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n展示出的江澤民事蹟，包括香港回歸、因應1998年金融危機、加入世貿組織（WTO）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099278/org/1c7b3d53d348f65714b06a06ca5dafa4.jpg/PrSbLCO7GsWZRgmV6jql2qQrjHygwNxkccVdF3HFXRc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099278%2Forg%2F1c7b3d53d348f65714b06a06ca5dafa4.jpg%2FPrSbLCO7GsWZRgmV6jql2qQrjHygwNxkccVdF3HFXRc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e673da04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡錦濤的事蹟則包括對抗SARS疫情及2008年汶川地震救災。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099280/org/a33c9641006199b14ffbff99a818dbfe.jpg/sba8SRNJNNFaUR5JfcsDTimJAuoorlQsv2kXAb9pFwE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099280%2Forg%2Fa33c9641006199b14ffbff99a818dbfe.jpg%2Fsba8SRNJNNFaUR5JfcsDTimJAuoorlQsv2kXAb9pFwE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=88b34453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即使是鄧小平、江澤民、胡錦濤的展示看板上，也都穿插著習近平的評語，至於其他5大展區，也有多處列出習近平講話摘錄，內容涉及環保、法治、文化等諸多方面。"}]}